<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Confirmación de Pedido - MONERO</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <style type="text/css">
      /* CLIENT-SPECIFIC STYLES */
      body,
      table,
      td,
      a {
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      }

      table,
      td {
        mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
        mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
      }

      img {
        -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
      }

      /* RESET STYLES */
      img {
        border: 0;
        height: auto;
        line-height: 100%;
        outline: none;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      table {
        border-collapse: collapse !important;
      }

      body {
        height: 100% !important;
        margin: 0 !important;
        padding: 0 !important;
        width: 100% !important;
      }

      /* iOS BLUE LINKS */
      a[x-apple-data-detectors] {
        color: inherit !important;
        text-decoration: none !important;
        font-size: inherit !important;
        font-family: inherit !important;
        font-weight: inherit !important;
        line-height: inherit !important;
      }

      /* MEDIA QUERIES */
      @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
        .mobile-hide {
          display: none !important;
        }

        .mobile-center {
          text-align: center !important;
        }
      }

      /* ANDROID CENTER FIX */
      div[style*='margin: 16px 0;'] {
        margin: 0 !important;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body
    style="
      margin: 0 !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      background-color: #f4efe9;
    "
    bgcolor="#f4efe9"
  >
    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="background-color: #f4efe9" bgcolor="#f4efe9">
          <table
            align="center"
            border="0"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            width="100%"
            style="max-width: 600px"
          >
            <!-- HEADER SECTION -->
            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                valign="top"
                style="font-size: 0; padding: 35px"
                bgcolor="#16302b"
              >
                <div
                  style="
                    display: inline-block;
                    max-width: 100%;
                    min-width: 100px;
                    vertical-align: top;
                    width: 100%;
                  "
                >
                  <table
                    align="center"
                    border="0"
                    cellpadding="0"
                    cellspacing="0"
                    width="100%"
                    style="max-width: 300px"
                  >
                    <tr>
                      <td
                        align="center"
                        valign="top"
                        style="
                          font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                          font-size: 36px;
                          font-weight: 800;
                          line-height: 48px;
                        "
                        class="mobile-center"
                      >
                        <h1
                          style="
                            font-size: 36px;
                            font-weight: 800;
                            margin: 0;
                            color: #f4efe9;
                            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
                          "
                        >
                          MONERO
                        </h1>
                        <p
                          style="
                            font-size: 14px;
                            font-weight: 400;
                            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
                            color: #f4efe9;
                          "
                        >
                          Confirmación de Pedido
                        </p>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- MAIN CONTENT SECTION -->
            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                style="padding: 35px 35px 20px 35px; background-color: #ffffff"
                bgcolor="#ffffff"
              >
                <table
                  align="center"
                  border="0"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  width="100%"
                  style="max-width: 600px"
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      align="center"
                      style="
                        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                        font-size: 16px;
                        font-weight: 400;
                        line-height: 24px;
                        padding-top: 25px;
                      "
                    >
                      <!-- LOGO - Using moneroget.com domain -->
                      <img
                        src="https://www.moneroget.com/logos/Logo-Monero.png"
                        width="120"
                        alt="MONERO"
                        style="display: block; border: 0"
                      />
                      <h2
                        style="
                          font-size: 28px;
                          font-weight: 800;
                          line-height: 36px;
                          color: #16302b;
                          margin: 20px 0 10px 0;
                        "
                      >
                        ¡Tu pedido ha sido confirmado!
                      </h2>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      align="center"
                      style="
                        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                        font-size: 16px;
                        font-weight: 400;
                        line-height: 24px;
                        padding-top: 10px;
                      "
                    >
                      <p
                        style="
                          font-size: 16px;
                          font-weight: 400;
                          line-height: 24px;
                          color: #555555;
                          margin: 0;
                        "
                      >
                        Gracias por tu compra. Tu pedido ha sido recibido y está
                        siendo procesado.
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>

                  <!-- ORDER DETAILS TABLE -->
                  <tr>
                    <td align="left" style="padding-top: 30px">
                      <table
                        cellspacing="0"
                        cellpadding="0"
                        border="0"
                        width="100%"
                      >
                        <tr>
                          <td
                            width="60%"
                            align="left"
                            bgcolor="#f4efe9"
                            style="
                              font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                              font-size: 16px;
                              font-weight: 800;
                              line-height: 24px;
                              padding: 12px;
                              color: #16302b;
                            "
                          >
                            Número de Pedido
                          </td>
                          <td
                            width="40%"
                            align="right"
                            bgcolor="#f4efe9"
                            style="
                              font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                              font-size: 16px;
                              font-weight: 800;
                              line-height: 24px;
                              padding: 12px;
                              color: #16302b;
                            "
                          >
                            {{orderNumber}}
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td
                            width="60%"
                            align="left"
                            style="
                              font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                              font-size: 16px;
                              font-weight: 400;
                              line-height: 24px;
                              padding: 15px 12px 5px 12px;
                              color: #333333;
                            "
                          >
                            Fecha del Pedido
                          </td>
                          <td
                            width="40%"
                            align="right"
                            style="
                              font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                              font-size: 16px;
                              font-weight: 400;
                              line-height: 24px;
                              padding: 15px 12px 5px 12px;
                              color: #333333;
                            "
                          >
                            {{orderDate}}
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                    </td>
                  </tr>

                  <!-- TOTAL SECTION -->
                  <tr>
                    <td align="left" style="padding-top: 25px">
                      <table
                        cellspacing="0"
                        cellpadding="0"
                        border="0"
                        width="100%"
                      >
                        <tr>
                          <td
                            width="60%"
                            align="left"
                            style="
                              font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                              font-size: 18px;
                              font-weight: 800;
                              line-height: 24px;
                              padding: 12px;
                              border-top: 3px solid #16302b;
                              border-bottom: 3px solid #16302b;
                              color: #16302b;
                            "
                          >
                            TOTAL
                          </td>
                          <td
                            width="40%"
                            align="right"
                            style="
                              font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                              font-size: 18px;
                              font-weight: 800;
                              line-height: 24px;
                              padding: 12px;
                              border-top: 3px solid #16302b;
                              border-bottom: 3px solid #16302b;
                              color: #16302b;
                            "
                          >
                            Bs. {{totalPrice}}
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- CUSTOMER INFO & SHIPPING SECTION -->
            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                height="100%"
                valign="top"
                width="100%"
                style="padding: 0 35px 35px 35px; background-color: #ffffff"
                bgcolor="#ffffff"
              >
                <table
                  align="center"
                  border="0"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  width="100%"
                  style="max-width: 600px"
                >
                  <tr>
                    <!-- CUSTOMER INFO COLUMN -->
                    <td
                      width="50%"
                      align="left"
                      valign="top"
                      style="
                        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                        font-size: 16px;
                        font-weight: 400;
                        line-height: 24px;
                        padding-top: 20px;
                        padding-right: 10px;
                      "
                    >
                      <p
                        style="
                          font-weight: 800;
                          color: #16302b;
                          margin: 0 0 10px 0;
                        "
                      >
                        Información del Cliente
                      </p>
                      <p style="margin: 0; color: #555555">{{customerName}}</p>
                      <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #555555">
                        {{customerEmail}}
                      </p>
                      <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #555555">
                        {{customerPhone}}
                      </p>
                    </td>

                    <!-- SHIPPING INFO COLUMN -->
                    <td
                      width="50%"
                      align="left"
                      valign="top"
                      style="
                        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                        font-size: 16px;
                        font-weight: 400;
                        line-height: 24px;
                        padding-top: 20px;
                        padding-left: 10px;
                      "
                    >
                      <p
                        style="
                          font-weight: 800;
                          color: #16302b;
                          margin: 0 0 10px 0;
                        "
                      >
                        Dirección de Envío
                      </p>
                      <p style="margin: 0; color: #555555">
                        {{shippingAddress}}
                      </p>
                      <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #555555">
                        {{shippingCity}}
                      </p>
                      <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #555555">
                        {{shippingCountry}}
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- SHIPPING METHOD SECTION -->
            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                style="padding: 0 35px 35px 35px; background-color: #ffffff"
                bgcolor="#ffffff"
              >
                <table
                  align="center"
                  border="0"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  width="100%"
                  style="max-width: 600px"
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      align="center"
                      style="
                        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                        font-size: 16px;
                        font-weight: 400;
                        line-height: 24px;
                        padding: 20px;
                        background-color: #f4efe9;
                        border-radius: 8px;
                      "
                    >
                      <p
                        style="
                          font-weight: 800;
                          color: #16302b;
                          margin: 0 0 10px 0;
                        "
                      >
                        Método de Envío
                      </p>
                      <p style="margin: 0; color: #555555">
                        {{shippingMethod}}
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- ORDER STATUS SECTION -->
            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                style="padding: 0 35px 35px 35px; background-color: #ffffff"
                bgcolor="#ffffff"
              >
                <table
                  align="center"
                  border="0"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  width="100%"
                  style="max-width: 600px"
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      align="center"
                      style="
                        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                        font-size: 16px;
                        font-weight: 400;
                        line-height: 24px;
                        padding: 20px;
                        border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
                      "
                    >
                      <p
                        style="
                          font-size: 14px;
                          color: #555555;
                          margin: 0 0 15px 0;
                        "
                      >
                        Recibirás un mensaje cuando tu pedido haya sido enviado.
                      </p>
                      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #555555; margin: 0">
                        Si tienes alguna pregunta, contáctanos a través de
                        nuestra página web.
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- FOOTER SECTION -->
    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#f4efe9" align="center">
          <table
            border="0"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            width="100%"
            style="max-width: 600px"
          >
            <tr>
              <td
                bgcolor="#f4efe9"
                align="center"
                style="
                  padding: 30px 30px 30px 30px;
                  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                  font-size: 14px;
                  font-weight: 400;
                  line-height: 18px;
                "
              >
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #555555">
                  Este correo fue enviado automáticamente desde
                  <a
                    href="https://www.moneroget.com"
                    style="
                      color: #16302b;
                      font-weight: 600;
                      text-decoration: none;
                    "
                    target="_blank"
                    >MONERO</a
                  >
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #777777; font-size: 12px">
                  © 2025 MONERO. Todos los derechos reservados.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>